                <p>The local retail facilities, as well as those further afield, are easily accessible. The LRT is minutes away in <a href="/brentwood.php">Brentwood</a>, and 14 St. NW crosses through Collingwood making it easy to travel the city. If you require services outside of the neighbourhood, you may easily obtain them by driving or via public transportation.</p>
