                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Parks &amp; Shopping &mdash;</h3>
                    <p>There are lots of activities to do and enjoy in this Northwestern Calgary neighbourhood, with Nose Hill Park on the north and Confederation Park on the south. </p>
                    <p>Collingwood, Brentwood, and <a href="/charleswood.php">Charleswood</a> are all members of the Triwood Community Association. The Triwood Community Centre, which features a multipurpose hall, ice rink, and 2 ball fields, is managed by the organization.</p>
                    <p>Triwood is a hub of activity and provides a diverse range of services for inhabitants of these Northwest communities. A dynamic and healthy community spirit is ensured by the community association, which conducts a playschool and playgroup, Kindermusik and kindergarten programs, Boy Scouts and Girl Guides, as well as a range of sports, fitness, and events for both the young and adult population. There are also neighbouring tot lots, sports arenas, and golf courses.</p>
                    <p>Triwood was the first neighbourhood to construct an arena, was vital in the introduction of Ringette to Calgary, and is host to the city's first senior slo pitch team. Thursday bingos, Seniors Tai Chi, dog training, and before and after school activities are all held in the community facility.</p>
                    <p>Other activities you can engage in as a resident of Collingwood include:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Collingwood is centrally located in Calgary's Northwestern corridor, just minutes from all of the city's main commercial centres. </li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 30px;">The neighbourhood is bordered by 14th Street, making travelling to the inner city a snap. Market Mall, is only a 5-minute drive away. </li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Homesense, The Bay, Sporting Life, Zara, and a slew of other well-known retailers can be found here. </li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Collingwood residents have easy access to schools, parks, and shopping, which are all just minutes away. </li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Sports aficionados will appreciate how near McMahon Stadium is to their house.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
