    <div style="margin-top: 80px;">
        <h2>General feel and vibe &mdash; What's it like living in Collingwood?</h2>
        <p>For individuals who want a laid-back ambience, Collingwood is a great place to buy a property. Overall, this region is relatively tranquil, as the streets are normally pretty quiet. Finally, parks are well-located, and there are several of them nearby for people to enjoy, making them very accessible from a variety of locations in this area of Calgary.</p>
        <p>The community is a favourite among people wanting to start families as well as university students due to its location and calm environment.</p>
